  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK955">
<l>vaḻaṅkuva tuḷvīḻntak kaṇṇum paḻaṅkuṭi</l>
<l>paṇpiṟ ṟalaippirita liṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though their means fall off, those born in ancient families, will not lose their character (for liberality).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
